  "remarks": "UEC-Saturn is a Russian military industry company. It manufactures engines for the Su-30, Su-35 and Su-57 military aircraft that are used by the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine. Furthermore, it produces engines for the Kh-101 strategic air-to-ground cruise missiles that are employed by the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation in Ukraine.",
